sequenceDiagram
    title Create ShortCourse

    participant Submit Learner Data
    participant Learner Data Outer
    participant Courses Api
    participant Learning Inner Api
    participant Earnings Inner Api

    Submit Learner Data ->> Learner Data Outer: CreateShortCourse (Post)

    Learner Data Outer ->> Courses Api: Get Courses Lookup (Get)

    Courses Api ->> Learner Data Outer : Ok 200 + Course Lookup Data
   

    alt No existing short course learning

        Learner Data Outer ->> Learning Inner Api: CreateDraftShortCourse (Post)

        Note over Learning Inner Api: Create learning

        Learning Inner Api ->> Learner Data Outer : Ok 200

        Learner Data Outer ->> Earnings Inner Api: CreateUnapprovedShortCourseLearning (Post)

        Note over Earnings Inner Api: Create earnings

        Earnings Inner Api ->> Learner Data Outer : Ok 200

    else Reinstating

        Learner Data Outer ->> Learning Inner Api: CreateDraftShortCourse (Post)

        Note over Learning Inner Api: Update and reinstate learning
        
        Learning Inner Api ->> Learner Data Outer : Ok 200

        Learner Data Outer ->> Earnings Inner Api: UpdateShortCourseOnProgramme (Put)

        Note over Earnings Inner Api: Update earnings

        Earnings Inner Api ->> Learner Data Outer : Ok 200
    end


    Learner Data Outer ->> Submit Learner Data: Accepted 202
